{"word":"μνημονεύω","slug":"μνημονεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μνημονεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μνήμων'><el>μνήμων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to call to mind, remember</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to call to</i> another's <i>mind, mention</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>memorare</el>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be remembered, had in memory</i>, <el>μνημονεύσεται χάρις</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>μνημονευθήσεται</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}